cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use M-AIDA in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "M-AIDA: Meta-Analysis Intelligent Data Assistant"
abstract: >-
  M-AIDA is a research software tool for international-business meta-analysis. It
  semi-automates the extraction of effect sizes (Pearson r, t, F, beta, p, N, CI)
  from academic PDFs using an LLM pipeline, with a human-in-the-loop verification
  dashboard for the principal investigator and an immutable data-lock workflow
  that exports a reproducible effect-size dataset for three-level meta-analysis.
type: software
version: "7.0.0"
date-released: "2026-06-08"
